{"tid":2314289,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"轉發「武肺疫苗讓童畸形」不認錯 漫威女星遭罵到IG關版","createTime":"2020-12-06T12:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T12:55:47.000Z","uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24d8d0e42383fc3199ab007e8187e046c09d2a59","tid":2314289,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"新冠疫情仍在歐美地區肆虐，網路上也開始出現各種危言聳聽的不實消息。在電影《黑豹》中，飾演男主角查德威克鮑斯曼（Chadwick Boseman）妹妹的蕾蒂夏萊特（Letitia Wright），日前竟分享質疑新冠疫苗的影片，其中荒謬言論引起公憤，甚至連同劇演員「戰爭機器」唐奇鐸（Don Cheadle）都忍不住砲轟。<br />\n<br />\n蕾蒂夏萊特分享的影片長達70分鐘，內容提及如果施打新冠疫苗的話，小孩會變成有11根手指或12根腳趾的畸形，不斷質疑新冠疫苗的安全性，然而此說話未獲得證實，在網路上頓時引起公憤，認為蕾蒂夏萊特是在散播不實謠言，連唐奇鐸都無奈發聲：「不會為分享這些資訊的人辯護，但我也不會棄她於不顧。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201206003311-260404?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201206003311-260404%3Fchdtv&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2gjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=a7c0afa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201206003311-260404?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"fc22d9dc2dc936cb9ffa0b338054fa9707f9710d","tid":2314289,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:28:07.000Z","msg":"打支那疫苗咪會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4d71f6684718c2f4ff048ec48b26a32fb02e12","tid":2314289,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"留名睇畸形"},{"pid":"2641dd2e24dacac69ccc881bc28c23cc47d53339","tid":2314289,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"同劇演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3341f1b863bbc5bddb2fd7c6901064b5c8974c88","tid":2314289,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2641dd2e24dacac69ccc881bc28c23cc47d53339","tid":2314289,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"同劇演員<img src=\"/a